OL,4,Crelated home insurance claims in 2023
OL,6,FHome insurance claims for weather-
OL,7,Frelated damage reached a record #573
OL,8,Fmillion last year, according to the
OL,9,FAssociation of British Insurers (ABI)
OL,10,Ffuelled by a .
OL,12,FThis was over a third (36%) higher
OL,13,Fthan in 2022, when the total was #421
OL,14,Fmillion.
OL,16,FThe rise was due to several storms,
OL,17,Fincluding Babet, Ciaran and Debi,
OL,18,Faccording to the association, whose
OL,19,Frecords on weather-related domestic
OL,20,Fclaims go back to 2017.
