OL,3,CRecord #573m paid out in weather-
OL,4,Crelated home insurance claims in 2023
OL,6,FWeather damage was not just a problem
OL,7,Ffor homeowners, with businesses
OL,8,Fincurring #443 million in weather
OL,9,Fclaims in 2023.
OL,11,FThe average weather-related payout for
OL,12,Fbusinesses last year was #18,542,
OL,13,Fjumping from #12,612 in 2022.
OL,15,FThe ABI said that property insurers
OL,16,Fhad typically paid out around #13
OL,17,Fmillion per day last year to help
OL,18,Fhomeowners and businesses cope with
OL,19,Fevents including flooding and theft.
