OL,6,FThe industry paid out #4.86 billion to
OL,7,Fhomeowners and businesses in 2023, the
OL,8,FABI said.
OL,10,FMore than half of this figure ` #2.55
OL,11,Fbillion ` was for home insurance
OL,12,Fclaims.
OL,14,FThe ABI said this total was up from
OL,15,F#2.33 billion in 2022 and was driven
OL,16,Fby weather-related damage.
