OL,6,FWhile the total number of claims
OL,7,Fremained fairly level, the average
OL,8,Fclaim paid to businesses and
OL,9,Fhomeowners rose to #6,235, an 11%
OL,10,Fincrease compared with 2022.
OL,12,FLouise Clark, policy adviser at the
OL,13,FABI said: "Extreme weather events may
OL,14,Fnot feel so rare as they used to as we
OL,15,Fgrapple with a changing climate.
